downscaleR 0.10-0
=================
* New function/object nomenclature (non-backwards compatibility)
  * In general, the term field is replaced by more generic 'grid'
* Fully independized from the loadeR bundle (yet highly recommended)
* Enabled parallelization (Linux and Mac OS only)
* Enhancements in perfect-prog downscaling
  * Parallel option
  * Cross validatin schemes
  * Monthly mean rescaling
* Function for flexible temporal aggregations
* Function for grid linear detrending
* Other minor bug fixes and enhancements



